9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1250, L.D. 1879, “An Act to Support
10 Maine's Agricultural Economy by Increasing Revenue from the Corporate Income Tax and
11 Providing Property Tax Exemptions”
12 Amend the bill by striking out the title and substituting the following:
13 'An Act to Support Maine's Agricultural Economy by Increasing Revenue from the
14 Corporate Income Tax'
15 Amend the bill in section 1 in subsection 7 in paragraph A in the last line (page 1, line
16 10 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "subsection." the following: 'The additional tax
17 must be apportioned pursuant to chapter 821 consistent with the requirements of
18 subsections 3 and 4.'
19 Amend the bill in section 1 in subsection 7 in paragraph C in the 2nd line (page 1, line
20 15 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "amounts" the following: ', with each fund or
21 program fully funded before funds are directed to the next priority fund or program,'
22 Amend the bill in section 1 in subsection 7 in paragraph C by striking out all of
23 subparagraphs (1) and (2) (page 1, lines 16 to 23 in L.D.).
24 Amend the bill in section 1 in subsection 7 in paragraph C by renumbering the
25 subparagraphs to read consecutively.
26 Amend the bill by striking out all of section 2 and inserting the following:
27 'Sec. 2. Appropriations and allocations. The following appropriations and
